title: Tierra Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Bakery, Catering, French, Spanish, African
description: Cafe/restaurant located in the town's cultural quarter. Warm, rustic feel inside, while outside is a sunny stream-side terrace. Brunch-lunch means freshly prepared dishes, coffee, juices and in-house-made cakes and pastries. Dinner means a weekly changing menu and twists on classics.
